welcome to the list!  welcome back to the split bus scene.  there are lots of 
people here, a fairly noisey list.

Topics that cause strife : lowering- think the topic was banned for a while 
because of all the strife

It is a sort of subset of the custom vs. stock resto schism.  Though it seems 
that the stock resto freaks get a fair share of dissing  (you'll hear 
"vintage nazi" a lot for anyone who is not pro custom), not just the folks 
who make a DD slammed sunroof panel dressed up tart out of what had once been 
a decent honest working bus.   Of course you gotta look at the freak show, 
but jeez, do you really want to LIVE with that?
that's the sort of stuff what you should'nt write.
tire topics roll around, but I don't pay much attention, so I dunno if people 
have such strong opinions about them

 feel free to post your engine building question/ comments, trip reports,etc 
you'll probably get several (possibly different) answers to any question.  :) 
 ANd there is lots in the archives, I hear.

